snippet.textDisplay:
That was funny as hell!! 😂
My wife took me to Vegas for my 40th birthday and got me on a party tour bus with a few dozen strangers. The last of the 3 clubs was at the Paris under the tower. My wife got bottle service at a huge table in the center of the club and invited EVERYONE on the party bus to join us for bottle service. THAT WAS A TAB!! 😂
My wife got trashed and threw up in one of the bottle service buckets that was filled with ice.
Last thing I remember is our security guard tapping me on my arm sayin, she can’t be here anymore. So we had to leave my part early. Fortunately we had a suit at the Paris hotel so we didn’t have far to stumble.
You can’t beat a 40th birthday party in Vegas!!
